As of the census<ref name="census2">{{cite web |title=U.S. Census website |url=https://www.census.gov |access-date=May 23, 2011 |publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref> of 2010, there were 253 people living in the CDP. There were 109 housing units. The [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|racial makeup]] of the town was 93.3% White, 0.8% Asian, 5.1% from some other race, and 0.8% from two or more races. Hispanic or Latino of any race were 9.9% of the population.

